sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server
    participant database

    browser->>server: User enters note content and clicks Save
    activate server
		server-->>browser: HTML document
		deactive server

    browser->>server: POST request to save new note
    server->>database: Add new note to database
    activate database
    database-->>server: Confirmation of note addition
    server-->>browser: Response indicating success
    deactivate database
    deactivate server

   
    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/notes
    activate server
    server-->>browser: Updated HTML document with new note
    deactivate server
